column5: is anyone getting any fish out there???? have been there 5 times this year and have not marked or seen any fish caught in the past i remember seeing lots of reports and pics and this year has been nothing
pm fishmaster. he wil guide you right.
Where have  you been fishing? Odd to not MARK any fish. My finder's usually solid fish everytime I'm there.. I just can't get them to bite.

the fish are in the water. If you are walking through Dunnville you will smell fish, but that is usually eminating from the residents. I have a cousin there that looks like a mudcat. Quite a town that Dunnville

lol yeah the majority is usually smelt if I turn the sensitivity to - 5 though a lot of bigguns still roam the bottom. Are they 'eyes or big old cats who knows.. but there are definitely fish in that river.. LOTS!
maybe my vex is broken  but in the past i was always marking fish

Ive been seeing lots of fish coming in ....and my Vex is marking fish ...were are you fishing ...if you look around you will see post with fish ...check out Grand River Ice Watch might be a few pages back...
